        "ROB_HUNK_ITEM_EFFECT_BACKUPMAG": "Gana <color=#00FF66>Municiones Falsas</color> despu\u00e9s de una recarga exitosa.",
        "ROB_HUNK_ITEM_EFFECT_BANDOLIER": "Los paquetes de municiones recargan tu cargador con <color=#00FF66>Municiones Falsas</color>.",
        "ROB_HUNK_ITEM_EFFECT_ALIENHEAD": "Gana <style=cIsUtility>m\u00e1s municiones</style> al recoger cualquier.",
        "ROB_HUNK_ITEM_EFFECT_BRAINSTALKS": "Mientras est\u00e1 activo, disparar tu arma <style=cIsUtility>no consume municiones</style>.",
        "ROB_HUNK_ITEM_EFFECT_LYSATECELL": "Gana <color=#00FF66>Municiones Falsas</color> al equipar un arma.",
        "ROB_HUNK_ITEM_EFFECT_PURITY": "Duplica el <style=cIsUtility>tama\u00f1o del cargador</style>. El consumo de municiones no cambia.",
        "ROB_HUNK_ITEM_EFFECT_LUMINOUSSHOT": "Gana una acumulaci\u00f3n despu\u00e9s de apuntar por <style=cIsUtility>1 segundo</style>. <style=cIsHealth>Pierde todas las acumulaciones al disparar o dejar de apuntar.</style>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_COMPLETION_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Segador",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_COMPLETION_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, vence el juego u obl\u00edtera. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_MONSOON_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Maestr\u00eda",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_MONSOON_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, vence el juego u obl\u00edtera en Monz\u00f3n. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_TYPHOON_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Gran Maestr\u00eda",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_TYPHOON_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, vence el juego u obl\u00edtera en Tif\u00f3n o Eclipse.\n<color=#8888>(Cuenta cualquier dificultad Tif\u00f3n o superior)</color> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_SUPPORTER_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Early Supporter",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_SUPPORTER_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Juega como HUNK antes del lanzamiento oficial. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_LIGHTWEIGHT_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Minimalista",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_LIGHTWEIGHT_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, completa la Etapa 1 sin objetos.\n<color=#8888>(Armas y herramientas no cuentan en tu contra)</color> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_GUERRILLA_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Bloqueado y Cargado",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_GUERRILLA_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, obt\u00e9n un arsenal completo. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_ROOKIE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Primer D\u00eda en el Trabajo",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_ROOKIE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, obt\u00e9n un arma nueva. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_SWAT_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Pacificador",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_SWAT_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, mejora completamente la MUP. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_CQC_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: CQC (Combate Cuerpo a Cuerpo)",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_CQC_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, realiza 10 contraataques exitosos en una Etapa. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_INFINITEKNIFE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: As de Picas",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_INFINITEKNIFE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, lleva dos Keycards de Picas al mismo tiempo. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_WESKERKNIFE_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Entusiasta de Armas de Fuego",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_WESKERKNIFE_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, mejora un arma con un nuevo accesorio. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_MACHETE_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: No Necesito Ninguna Arma",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_MACHETE_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, completa una Etapa sin disparar ninguna arma. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_RE4KNIFE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: El Camino Adelante",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_RE4KNIFE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, alcanza la Etapa 6. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_HOTDOGGER_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Qu\u00edmica B\u00e1sica",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_HOTDOGGER_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, obt\u00e9n el Lanzallamas Qu\u00edmico. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_STUNROD_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Oferta Tres por Uno",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_STUNROD_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, obt\u00e9n el Spark Shot. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_SSG_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Dominador",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_SSG_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, obt\u00e9n la SSG. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_FLAMER_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Pir\u00f3mano",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_FLAMER_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, mejora completamente el Lanzallamas Qu\u00edmico. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_SURVIVALKIT_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Sin Suerte Alguna",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_SURVIVALKIT_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, qu\u00e9date sin municiones en Commencement. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_JUMPPACK_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "HUNK: Sin Lugar a D\u00f3nde Ir Sino Hacia Arriba",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_ROB_HUNK_JUMPPACK_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Como HUNK, s\u00e9 v\u00edctima de un accidente de paracaidismo. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_NAME": "Nemesis T-Type",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_DESCRIPTION": "El Nemesis T-Type es un arma biol\u00f3gica imparable construida para resistir cualquier cantidad de castigo y neutralizar sus objetivos con facilidad.<color=#CCD3E0>\n\n< ! > Los saltos pueden cargarse para mayor distancia.\n\n< ! > Consumir enemigos te deja vulnerable, as\u00ed que encuentra un lugar seguro antes de hacerlo.\n\n< ! > La Biomasa aumenta tu da\u00f1o cuando est\u00e1 llena. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_SUBTITLE": "Arma Biol\u00f3gica Imparable",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..y as\u00ed parti\u00f3, todo bien.",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..y as\u00ed desapareci\u00f3, unidad humana ahora neutralizada.",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_DEFAULT_SKIN_NAME": "Predeterminado",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_CLASSIC_SKIN_NAME": "Cl\u00e1sico",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_VENOM_SKIN_NAME": "Simbiote",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_SUPER_SKIN_NAME": "<color=#FFFF00>Early Supporter</color>",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_MAHORAGA_SKIN_NAME": "Big Raga The Opp Stoppa",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_MINOS_SKIN_NAME": "King of Men",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_PASSIVE_NAME": "Forma de Vida Suprema",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsDamage>Causar da\u00f1o</style> almacena <style=cIsHealth>Biomasa</style>, aumentando tu <style=cIsDamage>da\u00f1o</style> cuando est\u00e1 llena. Los saltos pueden ser <style=cIsDamage>cargados</style> para <style=cIsUtility>saltos poderosos</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_PASSIVE2_NAME": "Armamento Biol\u00f3gico",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_PASSIVE2_DESCRIPTION": "El Nemesis T-Type puede <style=cIsHealth>mutar</style> consumiendo <style=cIsDamage>personas de inter\u00e9s</style>, ganando <style=cIsDamage>habilidades nuevas y mejoradas</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_PASSIVE22_NAME": "Aumento de Masa Muscular",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_PASSIVE22_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Ataques cuerpo a cuerpo</style> causan <style=cIsDamage>20%</style> m\u00e1s da\u00f1o, <style=isHealth>PERO los aliados pueden sufrir da\u00f1o</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_MELEE_NAME": "Agressi\u00f3n Brutal",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_MELEE_DESCRIPTION": "Pu\u00f1etazo para <style=cIsDamage>350% de da\u00f1o</style>. Usa mientras <style=cIsUtility>quieto</style> para pisotear para <style=cIsDamage>800% de da\u00f1o</style>. Usa mientras <style=cIsUtility>corriendo</style> para dar una embestida de hombro para <style=cIsDamage>600% de da\u00f1o</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_GRAB_NAME": "Alcance Mortal",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_GRAB_DESCRIPTION": "Agarra un enemigo. Usa Primario para consumirlo y curar 10% de la salud m\u00e1xima, o Secundario para cargar un lanzamiento de hasta 2.400% de da\u00f1o. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_DASH_NAME": "Embestida de Riesgo Biol\u00f3gico",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_DASH_DESCRIPTION": "Usa mientras <style=cIsUtility>en el aire</style> para avanzar en el aire <style=cIsDamage>una vez</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_ULTIMATE_NAME": "Masa Cr\u00edtica",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_BODY_ULTIMATE_DESCRIPTION": "Mant\u00e9n presionado para consumir lentamente <style=cIsHealth>Biomasa</style>, restaurando hasta <style=cIsHealing>100% de la salud m\u00e1xima</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_ITEM_EFFECT_TITLE": "Efecto Adicional",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_ITEM_EFFECT_BANDOLIER": "Los paquetes de municiones restauran <style=cIsHealth>10% de Biomasa</style>.",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_ITEM_EFFECT_ALIENHEAD": "Aumenta la <style=cIsHealth>Biomasa</style> ganada al <style=cIsDamage>consumir</style> enemigos.",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_ITEM_EFFECT_BRAINSTALKS": "Mientras est\u00e1 activo, la <style=cIsHealth>Biomasa</style> es <style=cIsUtility>ilimitada</style>.",
        "ROB_NEMESIS_ITEM_EFFECT_PURITY": "Aumenta la <style=cIsHealth>Biomasa</style> ganada <style=cIsDamage>al acertar</style>.",
        "ROB_ARTIFACT_PURSUER_NAME": "Artefacto del Perseguidor",
        "ROB_ARTIFACT_PURSUER_DESC": "Los jugadores comienzan la partida con un Distintivo S.T.A.R.S.",
        "ROB_ARTIFACT_CONTAMINATION_NAME": "Artefacto de la Contaminaci\u00f3n",
        "ROB_ARTIFACT_CONTAMINATION_DESC": "Cada jugador recibe un evento de Virus aleatorio cada Etapa.",
        "ROB_ARTIFACT_STRIKETEAM_NAME": "Artefacto del Escuadr\u00f3n",
        "ROB_ARTIFACT_STRIKETEAM_DESC": "Los jugadores ocasionalmente tendr\u00e1n Escuadrones de Ataque enviados para neutralizarlos.",
